      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Wall shear stress distribution — mesh sensitivity and experimental comparison",
      "description": "Wall shear stress distributions compared between three mesh refinement levels (3.2M, 6.8M, 14.1M cells) and available near-wall PIV data. Grid convergence index computed for WSS at critical impeller-volute interface. Experimental WSS derived from PIV velocity gradients at 1 mm wall-normal resolution. CFD predictions within experimental measurement uncertainty band for 83% of comparison locations. Donor-to-donor blood viscosity variability and temperature sensitivity of the blood analogue are noted in prose as sources of aleatory uncertainty but are not formally quantified or linked to a UQ artifact for this result.",
      "comparisonMetric": "Fraction of WSS comparison locations within experimental uncertainty band",
      "comparisonValue": "83%",
      "acceptanceCriterion": ">75% of locations within uncertainty band",
